Package clientSide.stubs

Class AssaultPartyStub

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientSide.stubs.AssaultPartyStub
  • public class AssaultPartyStub
extends java.lang.Object
    Stub to the Assault Party.

    It instantiates a remote reference to the Assault Party. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
